paragraphs.title: Clean up, create and populate Phoenix tables for timeseries

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)
//create a few over the existing HBase table
create view "timeseries"(
     "cf"."t"   varchar(10),
     "cf"."v" varchar(10),
      "cf"."id" varchar(100),
     "PKEY" varchar(100),
 CONSTRAINT pk PRIMARY KEY (PKEY)
)

%jdbc(phoenix)
//create a table with correct field data types
create table "phoenix-ts"(
 "timestamp" TimeStamp,
 "value" Decimal,
 "name" VARCHAR(100),
 "PKEY" VARCHAR(100)
 CONSTRAINT pk PRIMARY KEY (PKEY)
)
